com.esri.mo2.client.io
Class Authenticator

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--com.esri.mo2.client.io.Authenticator
public class Authenticator
extends Object

This class implements an object that is used to authenticate a service request. Authentication is performed by prompting the user for their login username and password.

Authentication can be either Basic and Digest.
